Package: zzrenvcheck
Title: Validate R Package Dependencies for Reproducibility
Version: 0.3.0
Authors@R:
    person("Ronald (Ryy) G", "Thomas", , "rgthomas@ucsd.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-1686-4965"))
Description: Validates that all R packages used in source code are properly
    declared in DESCRIPTION and locked in renv.lock for reproducibility.
    Provides automatic detection of package usage, dependency validation,
    and auto-fix capabilities through CRAN API integration.
